Celimax — Cica BHA Acne Foam Cleansing

A cleansing foam with salicylic acid designed for problem-prone skin affected by excess sebum, comedones, acne, and oily shine. Effectively removes sunscreen, makeup residue, and daily impurities while helping prevent clogged pores.

The foam provides multiple benefits:
- makeup removal;
- pore cleansing and reduction of sebaceous filaments;
- gentle exfoliation of dead skin cells;
- reduction of inflammation;
- prevention of dryness and tightness.

After cleansing, the skin feels fresh with a light tea tree scent, without stickiness or greasy residue. Suitable not only for oily and combination skin but also for sensitive skin, helping restore the skin microbiome and reduce redness.

Key ingredients: Panthenol (Vitamin B5); Salicylic Acid; Tea Tree Oil; Houttuynia Cordata Extract; Centella Asiatica; Bifida Ferment Lysate; Lactose

Composition/INCI: Bifida Ferment Lysate, Hydrogenated Polydecene, Disodium EDTA, Sorbitol, Oleic Acid, Lauric Acid, Potassium Benzoate, Panthenol, Salicylic Acid (0.45%), Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Myristic Acid, Stearic Acid, Polyquaternium-7, Potassium Hydroxide, Tea Tree Leaf Oil, Citric Acid, Glyceryl Stearate, Palmitic Acid, Propanediol, Sodium Citrate, Butylene Glycol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Water, Coco-Glucoside, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium Chloride, Centella Asiatica Extract (0.02%), Lactose, Sodium Benzoate, Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Disodium Coco-Glucoside Citrate, Arachidonic Acid, Madecassoside (0.001%), Glycerin, Houttuynia Cordata Extract

Be'Balance — Idebenone Microfiber Mask

A powerful antioxidant mask ideal for seasonal skin renewal. Idebenone helps brighten the skin from within, reduce pigmentation, deeply hydrate, and even out skin tone.

Key benefits of idebenone:
- up to 4 times more effective than vitamin C;
- up to 10 times more effective than coenzyme Q10;
- protects against environmental aggressors;
- improves complexion;
- slows down aging processes;
- nourishes and strengthens weakened skin;
- increases skin elasticity and firmness.

Liposomal delivery technology ensures deep penetration and maximum absorption of active ingredients. A patented complex of 17 amino acids supports collagen and elastin synthesis and long-lasting hydration.

Key ingredients: Botanical Extract Complex; Idebenone; Allantoin; Niacinamide; Ceramide NP

